Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.83,0:22:59.98,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.10,0:23:03.81,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离去远去
